    <note>Li Zhang [19561] CBD errs in including him as the same person as the waiqi Li Zhang [19289]. Zhang, who was the grandfather of Yi( [19562] and the person admired by Wang Anshi [1762] cited in the Wujun zhi, 26.14b and in Suzhou FZ, 77.23a was probably a nephew of Kan [19650] based on generational name, address and chronological logic. In addition, YLDD, 2368.5a identifies, in error, Zhang, as the grandfather of Yu [1121] instead of Yi, which almost proves a linkage and probably indicates an adoption.</note>
